		{
			description: ["Canvas is a crafted cloth item in Farmer's Delight — combine plant fibers and rope into panels of linen canvas. Canvas is used in wrapping recipes: wrap cooked meats and bread into portable meal packs, or produce Canvas-based table feasts that feed multiple players from a single placed block. The wrapping system turns individual food ingredients into packaged, high-saturation meal items that stack into manageable inventory footprints."]
