		{
			dependencies: ["CL01000000000001"]
			description: ["Straw is extracted from wheat using the Cutting Board — one of the core utility functions of that block beyond food preparation. Straws are used in Farmer's Delight drink recipes, where they serve as the vessel component for beverages assembled in the cooking pot. Tree Bark is similarly extracted from logs and used in Farmer's Respite tea recipes as a base ingredient. Batch both on a dedicated Cutting Board setup."]
			id: "CL01000000000002"
