		{
			dependencies: ["CL01000000000002"]
			description: ["The Cooking Pot produces soup, stew, and meal outputs in bulk — one batch yields multiple bowls. Farmer's Delight dishes compound saturation and hunger restoration beyond what vanilla food provides: Beef Stew restores more hunger than a steak; Vegetable Soup chains well with other meals. Cook five different Farmer's Delight cooking pot recipes and build a stocked larder before entering mid-game dungeons where food access is unreliable."]
			id: "CL01000000000003"
			rewards: [
