		}
		{
			dependencies: ["CL01000000000003"]
			description: ["Feast foods are Farmer's Delight recipes that place as a block on a surface and feed multiple players in sequence, like a cake. Each player right-clicks the feast to take one serving. Honey Glazed Ham, Roast Chicken Block, and other feasts provide the highest saturation-per-ingredient ratio in the mod. Building a feast and eating from it satisfies a long hunger bar in one action — useful for pre-raid buffing in multiplayer."]
			id: "CL01000000000004"
