		}
		{
			description: ["Farmer's Respite adds brewed teas, coffees, and hot drinks crafted in the Farmer's Delight Cooking Pot. Tea starts with Green Tea Leaves — harvested from green tea bushes that grow in forested and jungle biomes. The leaves can also be grown in a Botany Pot using a biome-appropriate soil. Stocking Green Tea Leaves unlocks the full Farmer's Respite drink tree, each drink providing different utility effects when consumed."]
			id: "CL01000000000005"
