		}
		{
			dependencies: ["CL01000000000005"]
			description: ["Green Tea is brewed in the Cooking Pot from Green Tea Leaves, water, and sugar. It provides Haste for a short duration when consumed — a meaningful early-combat buff for mining or timed encounters. Green Tea is among the easiest Farmer's Respite recipes to scale up: one Cooking Pot batch produces 16 units. Brew in bulk and keep a stack on hand before entering any dungeon where mining speed matters."]
			id: "CL01000000000006"
			rewards: [
