		}
		{
			dependencies: ["CL01000000000006"]
			description: ["Farmer's Respite teas diversify into temperature-spectrum brews. Long Yellow Tea — brewed from dried chamomile — provides Regeneration for a short window. Strong Hot Cocoa uses cocoa beans and milk to deliver Strength and slow movement speed reduction during combat. Both brew from the Cooking Pot in batches of 2. The Yellow Tea + Green Tea combination covers Haste and Regeneration simultaneously before a difficult encounter."]
			id: "CL01000000000007"
