		{
			dependencies: ["CL01000000000007"]
			description: ["Blazing Chili is Farmer's Respite's combat-focused drink — brewed from chili peppers, hot sauce, and blaze powder. It grants Fire Resistance and a burst of Speed for a short duration. Fire Resistance alone makes Blazing Chili mandatory before Nether runs or Blaze farming, removing the need for a separate Potion of Fire Resistance. Keep a stack when working in the EBF or Nether Fortress — no armor replaces immunity."]
