		{
			dependencies: ["CL01000000000008"]
			description: ["The advanced Farmer's Respite repertoire covers Coffee Cake Slice — a portable baked good brewed with coffee beans — and the Long-Brewing teas: Long Purulent Tea provides Poison Resistance; Long Dandelion Tea provides Night Vision. Brewing the full range of Farmer's Respite teas covers Fire Resistance, Haste, Regeneration, Strength, Night Vision, and Poison Resistance from a single mod. A stocked drinks chest replaces six different potion types."]
