		{
			description: ["Alex's Mobs adds wild game to the overworld — animals that do not fit vanilla's biome populations but provide unique food sources. Moose inhabit cold forests; their meat provides higher saturation than vanilla beef. Catfish are found in river and lake biomes; cooked catfish provide a strong saturation gain from an abundant source. Wild game hunting is a reliable mid-game food solution before Farmer's Delight farming is fully automated."]
