		{
			dependencies: ["CL01000000000010"]
			description: ["Cooked Moose Chop is obtained by cooking the raw Moose Chop dropped by Moose in cold forest biomes. It provides saturation comparable to a cooked steak but with higher hunger restoration, making it the strongest single-item food source from Alex's Mobs. Moose are non-aggressive unless provoked, making them easy to farm. A small enclosure with a lead and a grass floor will breed them indefinitely."]
