		{
			dependencies: ["CL01000000000010"]
			description: ["Catfish are found in rivers and freshwater lakes and can be caught with a standard fishing rod in addition to being killed directly. Cooked Catfish provides solid saturation and can be prepared on a Farmer's Delight Skillet over a stove, combining fish harvesting with the kitchen infrastructure already built for FD cooking. Catfish drop scales as a secondary material — these are used in Alex's Mobs crafting recipes for leather-equivalent armor pieces."]
